    }
   },
   "source": [
    "Parameter estimation: \n",
    "* $P(D|\\Theta)$ Choose parameters that maximize the probability of seeing the data\n",
    "* $P(\\Theta|D)$ Given the data choose the most probable parameters \n",
    "* $P(y|X)$ What's the probability of a class given the features"
   ]
